text: Launched first human trials in the Southern Hemisphere for a coronavirus vaccine. Melbourne is the beating heart of Australia’s internationally acclaimed medical research. Trials begin at the Alfred Hospital and Burnet Institute. #auspol #vicpol #springst https://t.co/Sa1VuWqGEe
